    "description": "About-<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this comical adventure, you embody Giles Outlandish, who drunkenly stumbles into a portal, mistaking it for an exit from a bar. Now trapped in Kayloo's Games, you must conquer diverse levels of various game genres to escape. However, the key to success lies in entertaining the mischievous creatures and avoiding the wrath of the monsters. With simple humor and clever thinking, players must navigate this whimsical realm to find a way back home before they become trapped forever.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGameplay-<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis Game Uses The Keyboard For Controls<br />\r\nWASD for movement, E to Interact, Shift to Run, Ctrl to Crouch<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore is to come in the future...",
